    0. <Object> Crate to loot to
    1. <Int>    Client ID
    2. <Bool>   Transfere done ( optional -Default: false)

    Return Value:
    <nil>

    Scope: Server
    Environment: Any
    Public: [No]
    Dependencies:

    Example:
        [cursorObject, clientOwner] remoteExecCall ["A3A_fnc_canLoot", 2];
        [_container, clientOwner, true] remoteExecCall ["A3A_fnc_canLoot", 2];

